{"tid":560353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺單身狗眼中，所有嘅情侶都係好似佢哋咁","createTime":"2018-02-14T04:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T04:55:18.000Z","uid":34129,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11fcb2dc8246b3b0bbfaa958fc1fd4f8f58cd8c3","tid":560353,"uid":34129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/121914_b61ee4727d0d1141f85e07a0b6d61004.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F121914_b61ee4727d0d1141f85e07a0b6d61004.png&h=fa14a7e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係情人節，對一堆單身狗嚟講，唔係一個值得慶祝嘅日子。<br />\n佢哋今日就算食飯，都只可以去吉野家大家樂果d一人邊爐，盡量避開街上無情嘅閃光。<br />\n然而，hk01呢間咁仆街嘅黨媒，竟然連毒撚們唯一嘅避難場所－網上世界－都唔放過，明明單嘢已經唔係新聞，竟然揀喺今日特登再做一條片嚟傷害我哋！明明只係諗住上網J吓結衣bb，點知一大堆friend whatsapp fb send條片過嚟！<br />\n<br />\n拍緊拖嘅女神J小姐：OMGWTFBBQ！嘩好核突呀！<br />\n已婚同事梁生：嘩好難頂呀！快d睇！<br />\n單身死黨阿俊：不能只有我看到！<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街！點解人類要互相傷害！呢d咩朋友嚟架？ 今日係情人節，send俾我係咪想講連李偲嫣都有人要，點解我無呀？我都只係想搵個好似結衣bb咁嘅女仔啫（講緊兩個求其一個都得喎），點解都搵唔到人嚟愛我呀？我想好好哋避世，過個安穩嘅年廿九都唔得嘅，係都要send嚟！點解！？<br />\n<br />\nJ小姐，喺你眼中覺得佢哋好核突，對我嚟講你哋都係一樣架咋，咪又係一男一女喺情人節book好曬晚餐癡癡纏纏！女神大晒呀，點解你要咁樣hurt我，你於心何忍呀？我話晒都幫你整過電腦吖？<br />\n<br />\n梁生，點解你咁bad taste，睇hk01都算，仲要睇完李偲嫣咁興奮開心share，何麥枒d流出唔見你有send俾我？屌你老母！（為咗之後要攞利是，當然冇講出口啦！）<br />\n<br />\n阿俊，你邊撚度俊呀！明明都係單身狗，識咗咁耐，點解要喺大家嘅傷口灑鹽！點解要互相傷害！我同你係無可能架！<br />\n<br />\n真係悲從中來！所以我決定。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/121902_24cbf69dc4505659120e277bc0e623f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F121902_24cbf69dc4505659120e277bc0e623f4.jpg&h=e18ee80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/159880/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E8%AB%87%E5%B0%81%E7%9B%A4-%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A%E5%A0%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%94%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E6%83%85%E7%AF%80-%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%87%E8%B7%A1-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F159880%2F-%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2581%25B2%25E5%25AB%25A3%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%259B%25A4-%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A9%259A%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B7%25A1-&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2BywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4ccfaa78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/159880/-%E6%83%85%E4%BA%BA%E7%AF%80-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E6%9D%8E%E5%81%B2%E5%AB%A3%E8%AB%87%E5%B0%81%E7%9B%A4-%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A%E5%A0%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%94%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E6%83%85%E7%AF%80-%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%87%E8%B7%A1-</a>"},{"pid":"1de2bdecc01e185137af1cc52dd4860390e56621","tid":560353,"uid":34129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"原文連結：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@chiuto/%E5%96%BA%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E7%8B%97%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD-%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%98%85%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E4%BD%A2%E5%93%8B%E5%92%81-c8f72d80d86f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40chiuto%2F%25E5%2596%25BA%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%258B%2597%25E7%259C%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2598%2585%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%2593%258B%25E5%2592%2581-c8f72d80d86f&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2BywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=eabbe90e\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@chiuto/%E5%96%BA%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E7%8B%97%E7%9C%BC%E4%B8%AD-%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%98%85%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E4%BD%A2%E5%93%8B%E5%92%81-c8f72d80d86f</a>"},{"pid":"dfde09bdd7042bb2a0214df96916d57f61aa0f7b","tid":560353,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T04:22:04.0